# Vercel is only serving the prebuilt `dist/` directory — exclude
# everything else from the upload to keep deploys fast.
#
# Gotcha: `*` excludes the `dist` directory itself; you must
# re-include both the directory (`!dist`) AND its contents
# (`!dist/**`), otherwise the negated content rule has no effect
# because the parent dir stays excluded.
*
!dist
!dist/**
!vercel.json
